ty-article/israeli-officials-seize-ap-equipment-halt-gaza-live-broadcast-citing-al-jazeera-law/0000018f-9b4e-dce9-a1cf-ffce461c0000</guid></item><item><title>校园抗议以色列的良性反犹太主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-virtuous-antisemitism-of-campus-protests-against-israel/0000018f-9aa0-d264-a1bf-deb7652f0000</link><description>示威者可以剥夺以色列人的生存权，因为在他们眼中，他们正在捍卫一个受到暴徒国家威胁的世界</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 12:32:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-virtuous-antisemitism-of-campus-protests-against-israel/0000018f-9aa0-d264-a1bf-deb7652f0000</guid></item><item><title>“姐妹，请原谅我们：”亲巴勒斯坦批评者对阿迈勒·克鲁尼对以色列加沙战争保持沉默感到遗憾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-critics-regret-bashing-amal-clooney-for-silence-on-israel-war-in-gaza/0000018f-9ab5-dce9-a1cf-fef5ad2f0000</link><description>推特批评者此前曾痛斥国际人权律师阿迈勒·克鲁尼没有就加沙局势发表任何公开声明，但当她加入国际刑事法院小组审查加沙战争罪行的消息曝光后，他们道歉并赞扬她</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 11:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-critics-regret-bashing-amal-clooney-for-silence-on-israel-war-in-gaza/0000018f-9ab5-dce9-a1cf-fef5ad2f0000</guid></item><item><title>医生恳求世卫组织利用影响力保障加沙人质的福祉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/doctors-implore-who-to-use-leverage-for-well-being-of-hostages-in-gaza/0000018f-9a87-d6da-a1cf-fba7506a0000</link><description>请愿书由两名以色列医生发起，他们呼吁世界卫生组织立即采取行动，确保人质的健康，目前全球有 1000 多名医生签署了该请愿书。一名医生痛惜道：“有一种感觉，世界正在忘记人质”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/doctors-implore-who-to-use-leverage-for-well-being-of-hostages-in-gaza/0000018f-9a87-d6da-a1cf-fba7506a0000</guid></item><item><title>八名巴勒斯坦人，包括骑自行车的青少年，在以色列军队袭击约旦河西岸城市杰宁时丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/seven-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-army-raid-in-west-bank-city-of-jenin/0000018f-9a9a-d6da-a1cf-fbba1e850000</link><description>以色列军方表示，已在杰宁启动反恐行动，并已确认至少15名受伤武装分子的身份。伊斯兰圣战组织宣布其特工正在参加战斗</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:18:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/seven-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-army-raid-in-west-bank-city-of-jenin/0000018f-9a9a-d6da-a1cf-fbba1e850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长表示，加沙的军事统治将把以色列国防军的义务兵役期延长至四年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-defense-minister-says-military-rule-in-gaza-would-extend-idf-service-to-4-years/0000018f-9a58-d6da-a1cf-fb7ae2ac0000</link><description>国防部长约阿夫·加兰特告诉利库德集团议员，以色列对加沙的军事统治将使军队付出沉重代价，并呼吁建立替代政府。他的同事批评他，称他试图将加沙交给巴勒斯坦权力机构</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-defense-minister-says-military-rule-in-gaza-would-extend-idf-service-to-4-years/0000018f-9a58-d6da-a1cf-fb7ae2ac0000</guid></item><item><title>美国国家安全顾问：沙特协议已完成；美国可能向以色列展示草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-advisor-saudi-deal-close-u-s-may-show-draft-to-israel/0000018f-9a0d-d35f-a1df-dfcd52110000</link><description>沙利文向以色列高级官员澄清，在升级沙特阿拉伯关系的协议方面已经取得进展，但表示担心内塔尼亚胡在巴勒斯坦问题上的立场会破坏谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-advisor-saudi-deal-close-u-s-may-show-draft-to-israel/0000018f-9a0d-d35f-a1df-dfcd52110000</guid></item><item><title>法国和德国表示支持国际刑事法院，不赞成对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特发出逮捕令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-back-icc-disapprove-of-arrest-warrants-for-netanyahu-gallant/0000018f-9a0d-d35f-a1df-d