rticle/.premium/israelis-react-to-raisi-crash-with-eli-copter-jokes-and-baklava/0000018f-9755-da35-a3af-d7ffe9e80000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院坚持不懈地对哈马斯和以色列领导人伸张正义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-20/ty-article/.highlight/the-iccs-unrelenting-pursuit-of-justice-against-hamas-and-israeli-leaders/0000018f-96fb-d376-a5bf-9efb9b4e0000</link><description>国际刑事法院可能永远失去以色列。但法院按照圣经的命令寻求并追求正义。如果这不能摧毁它，法庭可能会从世界其他地方赢得第二次机会</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 19:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-20/ty-article/.highlight/the-iccs-unrelenting-pursuit-of-justice-against-hamas-and-israeli-leaders/0000018f-96fb-d376-a5bf-9efb9b4e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：“新的反犹太主义已经从西方校园转移到海牙法庭”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-new-antisemitism-has-moved-from-campuses-of-the-west-to-court-in-the-hague/0000018f-96c3-da35-a3af-d7eb474a0000</link><description>以色列总理表示，在首席检察官卡里姆·汗向他、国防部长和三名哈马斯官员申请逮捕令后，整个国家都成为目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 17:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-new-antisemitism-has-moved-from-campuses-of-the-west-to-court-in-the-hague/0000018f-96c3-da35-a3af-d7eb474a0000</guid></item><item><title>“把它洒到路上”：以色列右翼活动分子如何组织起来阻止前往加沙的援助卡车</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-20/ty-article/.premium/how-right-wing-israeli-activists-are-organizing-to-block-aid-trucks-to-gaza/0000018f-965e-d35f-a1df-dfdf8e7d0000</link><description>一个极右翼运动正在派遣数百名年轻人干扰援助，他们威胁司机、破坏物品，而且不反对使用暴力。他们说他们得到了军方和警察提供的信息的帮助</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 17:16:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-20/ty-article/.premium/how-right-wing-israeli-activists-are-organizing-to-block-aid-trucks-to-gaza/0000018f-965e-d35f-a1df-dfdf8e7d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 227 天：卡塔尔部长称没有达成停火的政治意愿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-227-no-political-will-to-reach-cease-fire-qatari-minister-says/0000018f-96f5-d376-a5bf-9efdf2d00001</link><description>国际刑事法院检察官宣布，他正在寻求对以色列和哈马斯领导人涉嫌战争罪的逮捕令 ■ 卡塔尔国务部长：没有在加沙达成停火的政治意愿 ■ 以色列国防军评估加沙的战斗将至少再持续六个月 ■ 以色列的国防部长告诉美国国家安全顾问沙利文 以色列致力于扩大其拉法地面行动 ■ 战争进入 227 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 17:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-227-no-political-will-to-reach-cease-fire-qatari-minister-says/0000018f-96f5-d376-a5bf-9efdf2d00001</guid></item></channel></rss>